LongDescription:
<
You are in a dark room with a zombie, armed only with a torch and with only one goal: survive.
The inaccuracies inherent in all real time ray casting applications cast eery ripples along the walls.
This is an application of ray casting demonstrated in {shadows, link: shadows}.
>
